Class AeUnstructuredDeploymentLog

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AeFileDeploymentLoggerFactory.AeFileLogger
public class AeUnstructuredDeploymentLog
extends AeDeploymentLog

Provides an unstructured deployment log base class. The unstructured deployment logger simply writes all log messages to a PrintWriter (or the class can be extended to provide some other implementation of the writeMessage method.
